ore":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"又肚痛又頭痛，不如示範下點撚樣可以用lan線打結同咩lan線牌子咁撚勁可以上吊唔斷先啦<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味遲早你旺揚咁"},{"pid":"e362179aa78d1e0d23a2e945d5c8b1b39616019c","tid":882123,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d736520e67a0234fc79d811b92a73ce0f3f46a0","tid":882123,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:07:12.000Z","msg":"呀SIR做嘢唔駛你教"},{"pid":"a62364cfabf806d6856e638e9f020d06160f961e","tid":882123,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcd399728442675c5df9e704847a0bb3aa38a6b","tid":882123,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"成班虛假文書都唔需要上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f192d04b1cb603202a9c2fd1f8a9f159c162ad39","tid":882123,"uid":19287,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"79922cecf9304f45cfbb60f95e64a368b2e9f7c2","tid":882123,"uid":27664,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:12:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 嚟啲警員上庭問答仲好睇過電視戲劇 </span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"如果市民比佢地盤個陣咁答，可能比佢地打到仆街"},{"pid":"aa4f6579e157d5584c6a87d4489f8d9138d1c1bf","tid":882123,"uid":40855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"入過狗屋，唔好話定時定候無人巡房，就算喺倉敲閘敲到拆天，慈母都唔會入嚟，係得派餐或攞人先會見到佢哋"},{"pid":"24b179a780e82e5227ad873a79f04a69d2da6ced","tid":882123,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"上庭又講大話都唔拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b239406e1bb23176a7231ffea0cc58bba30a0e3","tid":882123,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a18b62301eb683e230af74c8945d828921f16fb","tid":882123,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e61cc17f2f79bb7049357cce63a6dcdcd6772097","tid":882123,"uid":49359,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:42:54.000Z","msg":"聽聞有過部門<br />\n全部人返功填早收工寫遲<br />\n最後有人玩野投訴<br />\n要睇cctv<br />\n但最後都係無事無人<br />\n只係要準時返工放工<br />\n實際成個部門都係虛假文書"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:23:24.000Z","msg":"冇呃ot掛"},{"pid":"eb14874fc04358551b4bd8dcea2cd196331bf075","tid":882123,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95b83be58bea968e415959ea45d07216c9559ab","tid":882123,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79922cecf9304f45cfbb60f95e64a368b2e9f7c2","tid":882123,"uid":27664,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:12:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 嚟啲警員上庭問答仲好睇過電視戲劇 </span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"答辯啲表現就快柒過tvb啲傻閪犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTvb啲戲終於開始貼地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}